title: [Maelstrom Bay, Bottom]
description: The uneven floor of the bay is dotted with clumps of seaweed and tall, tree-like clusters of elkhorn coral.  The floor of the bay rises sharply to the south.  A rocky wall, covered with bladder rockweed, emerges abruptly from the sandy bay floor to the east.
paths: Obvious exits: north, west, northwest, up
